  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/87d1ee7c06f64dc82db7dd3b7d6bb3f4.avif?t=1731343977\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Use your computer to order different types of booster packs from an online store. Open one pack after another in this relaxing card collection game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.poster.avif?t=1731343977\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.webm?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.mp4?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Buy packs from different collections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Premium booster packs with high chance of exclusive rare variants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Booster boxes with a lot of packs for less money.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relaxing pack opening gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/712f51fee1c3dd8cb2c5ce8982295231.avif?t=1731343977\" width=616 height=100 /></span>As an avid card collector, you will end up with a big collection of cards, sell your duplicates and your rarest cards for profit in a webpage. Manage your economy and get the best deals in a changing trading card market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/69cfdc7a6136d549f16a1e6836281127.poster.avif?t=1731343977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/69cfdc7a6136d549f16a1e6836281127.webm?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/69cfdc7a6136d549f16a1e6836281127.mp4?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use your retro computer to sell cards in an online store.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A dynamic card market, the price of the cards change over time, sell at the right time to maximize your profit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage your economy, ¿Will you sell that rare card for a lot of money or will you keep it for your collection?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/2e2820ef4688daa17a2f6563254a3e94.avif?t=1731343977\" width=616 height=100 /></span>As a card collecting enthusiast you will have different collections to complete, each one with hundreds of cards and rare variants with high value.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/bf986be2d6b8c6d1ba728efb3a1b423e.poster.avif?t=1731343977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/bf986be2d6b8c6d1ba728efb3a1b423e.webm?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/bf986be2d6b8c6d1ba728efb3a1b423e.mp4?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Complete up to 5 different card collections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hundreds of cards with rare variants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Scroll through your collection albums and inspect your precious trading cards.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/87d1ee7c06f64dc82db7dd3b7d6bb3f4.avif?t=1731343977\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Use your computer to order different types of booster packs from an online store. Open one pack after another in this relaxing card collection game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.poster.avif?t=1731343977\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.webm?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.mp4?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Buy packs from different collections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Premium booster packs with high chance of exclusive rare variants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Booster boxes with a lot of packs for less money.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relaxing pack opening gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/712f51fee1c3dd8cb2c5ce8982295231.avif?t=1731343977\" width=616 height=100 /></span>As an avid card collector, you will end up with a big collection of cards, sell your duplicates and your rarest cards for profit in a webpage. Manage your economy and get the best deals in a changing trading card market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"