vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981330/extras/bf986be2d6b8c6d1ba728efb3a1b423e.mp4?t=1731343977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Complete up to 5 different card collections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hundreds of cards with rare variants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Scroll through your collection albums and inspect your precious trading cards.</p></li></ul>",
